These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: american, australian, german, japanese, malaysian, mexican, polish
7 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, go, billiard, domino, whist, monopoly
 1. the american is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 2. the german is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 3. the polish is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 5. the australian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the japanese##1
 7. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the polish is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
11. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
12. the malaysian is on the left of the mexican##1
13. the mexican is in the middle##1
14. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the german##5
15. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
16. the person playing domino is not the polish##6
17. the american is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
18. the person playing backgammon is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | american | japanese | malaysian | mexican | polish | german | australian |
| Pet           | billiard   | whist    | monopoly       | scrabble     | go    | domino   | backgammon |

