City: boston, new-york, prague, london, nizza, hamburg, colone
 1. the person traveling to london is not the fan d&b##6
 2. the person traveling to nizza is not the fan d&b##6
 3. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5
 4. the fan house is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
 6. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
 9. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the fan d&b##5
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
11. the fan hip-hop is not the person traveling to prague##6
12. the fan classical is on the far right##1
13. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
14. the fan house is the person traveling to hamburg##1
15. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the fan house##1
16. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
17. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan house##1
18. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
19. the fan d&b is on the right of the fan trance##1
20. the fan soul is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
21. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
