 9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
10. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person driving the airplane is not the person watching animation movies##6
14. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
15. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
