 3. the person who likes azure is not the journalist##6
 4. the videographer is on the left or right of the manager##3
 5. the lawyer is on the left of the coach##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
 7. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 8. the journalist is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes azure##2
 9. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
11. the person who likes apricot is between the security-guard and the videographer##2
12. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
13. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
14. the person who likes turquise is the videographer##1
15. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
16. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
17. the coach is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |      5       |    6    |       7        |
| Job           | lawyer    | coach     | entrepreneur | journalist | videographer | manager | security-guard |
| Nationality   | lavender | blue | azure     | yellow   | turquise      | apricot  | lilac      |

